file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Example
paths:
  /some-path:
    get:
      summary: Get something
      operationId: getSomething
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Something"
components:
  schemas:
    Something:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - uuid
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        uuid:
          type: string
          format: uuid
